<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/ico" href="/images/icon.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('layouts/header'); -%>
    <%- include('layouts/nav_index'); -%>        

    <div class="container col-md-7" style="margin-top: 50px;">
        <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="/images/skiing2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Winter Life" height="480">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="background-color: rgba(75, 74, 74, 0.438);">
            <h5>Winter Life</h5>
            <p>Most fun in winter is playing with SNOW.</p>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/lake2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Nature Beauty" height="480">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="background-color: rgba(75, 74, 74, 0.438);">
            <h5>Nature Beauty</h5>
            <p>That's why we travell and seek thousands miles.</p>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/summerFlower.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Poem Time" height="480">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="background-color: rgba(75, 74, 74, 0.438);">
            <h5>Poem Time</h5>
            <p>Leaving some moment for thinking and reading.</p>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

<div class="container col-md-9" style="margin-top: 50px;">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <img src="/article_images/family_skiing.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." height="180px">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Family Skiing With Kids</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Skiing has become favorite winter family activity. Yes, skiing can be an enriching experience for both kids and adults</p>
                  <a href="/article/5fca89adb6a7083104f64f48/detail" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Reading more</a>
                </div>
              </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <img src="/article_images/blue-green-turquoise-water-of-lake-louise-early-july.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." height="180px">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Lake Louise</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Lake Louise is not only one of the largest Great Lakes; it is the largest body of fresh water on Earth. Let's sailing on it.</p>
                  <a href="/article/5fca76b4c0fc152ae86029c3/detail" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Reading more</a>
                </div>
              </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <img src="/article_images/tiger-burning-bright.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." height="180px">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Poem--“The Tiger”</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Tiger Tiger, burning bright / In the forests of the night / What immortal hand or eye / Could frame thy fearful symmetry?</p>
                  <a href="/article/5fca91afb6a7083104f64f4b/detail" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Reading more</a>
                </div>
             </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    <div class="container col-md-9" style="margin-top: 50px;">
            <% for( var article of articles  ) {
                %>                        
                <div class="row no-gutters border rounded overflow-hidden flex-md-row mb-4 shadow-sm h-md-250 position-relative">
                    <div class="col p-4 d-flex flex-column position-static">
                        <a href="/article/<%= article._id %>/detail"><h4 class="mb-0"><%= article.title %></h4></a>
                        <div class="mb-1 text-muted"><%= article.author %></div>
                            <p class="card-text mb-auto"><%= article.abstract %></p> 
                        </div>                       
                        <img src="/article_images/<%= article.image %>" class="rounded float-right" alt="article image" height="150px" width="200px">
                    </div>
                <%
                } 
            %>
    </div>
</div>
<%- include('layouts/footer'); -%>
</body>
</html>